  "description": "Variation of conditions 2 (Approved Plans) of planning permission ref: 13267/APP/2018/1873 dated 08/08/2018 to include a dormer on the front cat slide roof, alterations to rear dormers and changing glass porch panel to brick wall (Two storey rear extension, porch to front and conversion of roofspace to habitable use, to include raising of ridge, conversion of both sides of roof from hip to gable end, 3 rear dormers and 3 front rooflights)",
  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposals include the introduction of a front dormer and the reduction of the number of dormers to the rear, which did not form part of the original planning permission Ref: 13267/APP/2018/1873. These amendments would result in an alteration to the description of the development originally approved and as such, the proposal cannot constitute a minor amendment under S73 of the Town and Country Planning Act. Therefore a full planning application is required for the proposed development."
